{{#if user}}
  <p>Hello
    <b>{{user}}</b>
  </p>
  <p>Visit your personal profile to create your code snippets, delete or modify
    them as you please.
  </p>
{{/if}}

{{#unless user}}
  <p>Press
    <a href='/login'>login</a>
    if you have an account or
    <a href='/signup'>sign up</a>
    to create one
  </p>
  <p>Please authenticate in order to check all the content</p>
  <p>Snippets gives you the opportunity to create and modify your own code
    snippets, so if you want an alternative to the mainstreams GitHub or GitLab
    this is the place for you.</p>
{{/unless}}